        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Granulated blast furnace slag main use is as a alternative constitutents for cement production. It is here assumed that 30% of GBFS goes to the generic market for supplementary cementitious materials (SCMs). GBFS is one of the main SCMs used today. The production volume of GBFS is taken from the PV of the regional production activity (accessed 17th June 2019).</productionVolumeComment>
